Dialogue: 9,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aproximadamente duzentos.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,É vinte vezes mais longo que a Sidonia.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oito mil vezes o nosso volume!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que é tão enorme?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}O míssil antiplaneta...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele vai nos alcançar mais tarde.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:14.65,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,E esta batalha será sob a gravidade do planeta anão.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:18.24,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ter que carregar tudo isso e lutar em condições de gravidade não ajuda a taxa de sobrevivência.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolva a formação!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.12,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Orbitar os Gauna!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Canhões Heigus na superfície!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:38.52,0:00:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fui atingido!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:39.19,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não consigo ver nada! Não consigo fazer isso!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.85,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Comunicação com o comandante do Platoon 2 perdida!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}702...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: [T0]...[T1]Benisuzume...]
Dialogue: 9,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,É impossível!\NNão conseguimos desviar dele!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perdemos todo contato com o pelotão 2.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Eles foram aniquilados...
Dialogue: 9,0:01:01.08,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma hora até o impacto do míssil.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,O míssil fará\Najustes finais de curso.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:07.71,0:01:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidonia disparará seu canhão Super Heigus\Npara abrir um buraco na cabeça do G542.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrem por esse buraco\Ne acabem com o Gauna Mestre.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos que fazer isso!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparar para disparar.
