Dialogue: 9,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dez segundos até o impacto.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano massivo à placenta do G542!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Interior exposto.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucesso total!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ondas de choque se espalhando.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:28.53,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A interferência da Partícula Heigus está afetando as comunicações mais do que o esperado.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, vocês conseguem me ouvir?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataquem imediatamente!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.05,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.83,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo suficiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo controlar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Tanikaze!]
