Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano massivo à placenta de G542!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.70,0:04:24.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnZekton Rg\fax-0.19\fs47\blur0.7\frx12\fry348\c&H4145EF&\frz348.2\pos(608,299.8)}Link Perdido
Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Interior exposto.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucesso total!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataquem imediatamente.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde está Nagate?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuidem dos feridos e dos danificados!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você vai fazer, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:42.30,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumori tem o sistema de propulsão de mochila protótipo.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu consigo chegar a tempo se eu for sozinho!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: [T0]...[T1]Tanikaze...]
Dialogue: 9,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,É você que pega todo o equipamento especial de novo, hein?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Não é justo.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,É por isso que vou sozinho.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Aqui...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava guardando este tiro para vingar Hou.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:10.41,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tomará minha vingança?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pode contar comigo.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A placenta está regenerando!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Três minutos até o buraco ser selado!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: [T0]...[T1]Nagate...]
Dialogue: 9,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O canhão Heigus ainda não foi totalmente recarregado.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,O Pelotão 1 entrará nos Gaunas através do buraco!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Resposta dos Gaunas!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectado Gauna de alta velocidade!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,É o Benisuzume!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pare!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A gente consegue escapar disso!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ah, não...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos tão perto.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu entro, Samari!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiquem para trás!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Tsugumori!]
Dialogue: 9,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixem isso comigo.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá acabar com o Gauna Mestre!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas você está sozinho!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumori tem um revestimento anti-Heigus.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A placenta está regenerando muito rapidamente!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:48.26,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as estruturas, rompam!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A abertura está totalmente fechada!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Link perdido!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os relatórios cessarão!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Realocando partículas Heigus para áreas residenciais.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo que podemos fazer agora é rezar, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aproximadamente vinte minutos até que o G542 passe pela linha de interdição.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Não nos restam muitas munições!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guardem algumas munições para o Gauna Mestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mudar para os canhões de partículas Heigus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstrução próxima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinze minutos até o impacto! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinze minutos até o impacto do míssil antiplaneta.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reação de G542.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A densidade de Higgs na cabeça está subindo demais!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}O quê...?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele está tentando derrubar o míssil antiplaneta?!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze {**-san}!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano insignificante à estrutura.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No entanto, o piloto está inconsciente!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ele vai cair...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há nada que possamos fazer nessa altitude!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Tanikaze!]
Dialogue: 9,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Nagate!]
Dialogue: 9,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: [T0]...[T1]Izana[T2]...]
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A estrutura de Shinatose atingiu o limite de carga.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O motor está prestes a sobrecarregar.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Nagate!]
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Acorde!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Nagate!]
Dialogue: 9,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,O motor irá sobrecarregar.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Izana[T0]!]
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou desistir de Nagate!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é a luz de esperança de Sidonia!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinatose está ganhando altitude.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles estão se afastando\Nda superfície de G542.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{bg}Graças a Deus...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{bg}Uau...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Benisuzume está rapidamente\Nse aproximando de Shinatose!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Reação de Partícula Heigus de alta densidade\Nde Benisuzume!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai daí, Izana{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Izana!]
Dialogue: 9,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dez minutos até o impacto dos mísseis!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O Mestre Gauna está além daquele muro!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos que tentar destruí-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Seii!]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós não vamos conseguir!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos abaixo de 10% no armazenamento de partículas Heigus!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.16,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há necessidade de economizar partículas para o caminho de volta.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabe o que eu quero dizer?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Está aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse é o Gauna Mestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Está aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquele é o Gauna Mestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispersem!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,O míssil passou pela linha de interdição final.{final chance for Gauna to intercept}
Dialogue: 9,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cinco minutos até o impacto!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,E o pelotão um?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem resposta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenham distância das extremidades nas paredes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Erramos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Há muitos apêndices!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos que fechar a distância!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Não desista!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Procure um ângulo melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Coma isso!
