Dialogue: 9,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumori está sem munição de CPP!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A placenta de Benisuzume regenerou completamente!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze {**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Espera, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava guardando este disparo para vingar Hou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tomará minha vingança?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Falando Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um quadro gravemente danificado.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A aceleradora de Tanikaze está gravemente danificada.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Benisuzume está se aproximando.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Você é...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...nem Hoshijiro, nem humano!{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}
Dialogue: 9,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pega isto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A parede é muito grossa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Comandante!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos recuar e reagrupar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo para isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Se não chegarmos a tempo, Sidônia está perdida!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Samari, vou tentar disparar o canhão de Partícula Heigus na potência máxima de perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou chegar mais perto da unidade central,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,e arrancar um dos apêndices.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai morrer se sua unidade desligar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Neste momento, todos estão em perigo de morte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Tsuruuchi!]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quase foi cortado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem feito, Tsuruuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Coma isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ERRO_TRADUCAO: Tsuruuchi!]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Placenta está aberta!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Desintegração da bolha do G542 confirmada.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo até o impacto do míssil?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Menos de dois minutos.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda sem sinal IFF!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles ainda estão lá dentro!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que entrem em formação,\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}eu não posso dizer se—
Dialogue: 9,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles vão conseguir!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que sim!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuem monitorando-os!
